\q2 \w and|strong="H7725"\w* \w they|strong="H5971"\w* \w will|strong="H5971"\w* \w not|strong="H2088"\w* \w understand|strong="H8085"\w* \w it|strong="H7725"\w*,  
\q1 \w and|strong="H7725"\w* \w they|strong="H5971"\w* \w will|strong="H5971"\w* \w not|strong="H2088"\w* \w turn|strong="H7725"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w me|strong="H7725"\w*  
\q2 \w and|strong="H7725"\w* \w be|strong="H3820"\w* saved \add from being punished\add*.”   
\p
\v 11 Then \w I|strong="H5704"\w* said, “\w How|strong="H4970"\w* \w long|strong="H5704"\w* \add do you want me to continue to do that\add*?”  
\q1 \w He|strong="H5704"\w* replied, “\add Do it\add* \w until|strong="H5704"\w* \w their|strong="H3427"\w* \w cities|strong="H5892"\w* \w are|strong="H5892"\w* \w ruined|strong="H8077"\w* \add by their enemies\add*,  
