\v 12  \add Do it\add* \w until|strong="H3068"\w* \w I|strong="H3068"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* ◄exiled everyone/forced everyone \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w go|strong="H7368"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w their|strong="H3068"\w* enemies’ lands► \w far|strong="H7368"\w* \w away|strong="H7368"\w*,  
