\v 13 \w If|strong="H1961"\w* \add even\add* \w one|strong="H1961"\w* \w tenth|strong="H6224"\w* \add of the people survive and\add* stay \w there|strong="H1961"\w*,  
\q2 \add their enemies\add* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \add invade the land again and\add* \w burn|strong="H1197"\w* everything.  
