\c 21  
\s1 A message about the destruction of Babylon  
\p
\v 1  \add I received\add* \w this|strong="H3372"\w* \w message|strong="H4853"\w* \add from Yahweh about Babylonia\add*, \add a land that is\add* near \w the|strong="H3372"\w* \add Persian\add* Gulf \add but which will soon be\add* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w desert|strong="H4057"\w*.  
