\p
\v 14  \add So\add* \w the|strong="H3069"\w* Commander \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3069"\w* \w armies|strong="H6635"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* angels \w revealed|strong="H1540"\w* \w this|strong="H2088"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w me|strong="H4191"\w*: “\w I|strong="H5704"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w never|strong="H5704"\w* \w forgive|strong="H3722"\w* \w my|strong="H3068"\w* people \w for|strong="H5704"\w* sinning \w like|strong="H4191"\w* \w this|strong="H2088"\w*!”   
\s1 A message for Shebna  
\p
\v 15 \w The|strong="H5921"\w* Commander \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w armies|strong="H6635"\w* \w of|strong="H1004"\w* angels said \w this|strong="H2088"\w* \add to me\add*: “\w Go|strong="H3212"\w* \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w Shebna|strong="H7644"\w*, \w the|strong="H5921"\w* official \w who|strong="H6635"\w* \w supervises|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* workers \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w palace|strong="H1004"\w*, \w and|strong="H1004"\w* give \w this|strong="H2088"\w* message \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w him|strong="H5921"\w*:   
\q1
\v 16 '\add Who do you think you are?\add*  
\q2 \w Who|strong="H4310"\w* gave \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* authority \w to|strong="H3588"\w* build \w a|strong="H3068"\w* beautiful \w tomb|strong="H6913"\w* \w where|strong="H4100"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H4310"\w* \w be|strong="H3588"\w* buried,  
\q2 chiseling \w it|strong="H3588"\w* \w out|strong="H2672"\w* \w of|strong="H6913"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w rocky|strong="H5553"\w* \w cliff|strong="H5553"\w* \w high|strong="H4791"\w* \w above|strong="H4791"\w* \w this|strong="H3588"\w* valley?   
\q1
\v 17 \w You|strong="H2904"\w* \add think that you are\add* [IRO] \w a|strong="H3068"\w* great \w man|strong="H1397"\w*, \w but|strong="H2009"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w about|strong="H2009"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w hurl|strong="H2904"\w* \w you|strong="H2904"\w* \w away|strong="H2904"\w*.  
\q2 \add It will be as though\add* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* seize \w you|strong="H2904"\w*,   
\q1
\v 18 \w and|strong="H3027"\w* \w roll|strong="H6801"\w*/crumple \w you|strong="H3027"\w* \w into|strong="H3027"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w ball|strong="H1754"\w*  
\q2 \w and|strong="H3027"\w* throw \w you|strong="H3027"\w* away \w into|strong="H3027"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w large|strong="H7342"\w* distant land.  
\q1 \w You|strong="H3027"\w* \w will|strong="H1004"\w* \w die|strong="H4191"\w* \add and be buried\add* \w there|strong="H8033"\w*,  
\q2 \w and|strong="H3027"\w* \w your|strong="H3027"\w* beautiful \w chariots|strong="H4818"\w* \w will|strong="H1004"\w* stay \w there|strong="H8033"\w* \add in the hands of your enemies\add*.  
\q2 \w And|strong="H3027"\w* \add because of what happens to you\add*, \w your|strong="H3027"\w* master, \add the king\add*, \w will|strong="H1004"\w* \w be|strong="H4191"\w* \add very\add* ashamed/disgraced.   
\q1
\v 19 \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* will \w force|strong="H2040"\w* \w you|strong="H2040"\w* \w to|strong="H2040"\w* quit working in \w the|strong="H2040"\w* palace;  
\q2 \w you|strong="H2040"\w* will be demoted \w from|strong="H1920"\w* \w your|strong="H2040"\w* important position.   
\p
\v 20 \w Then|strong="H1961"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w summon|strong="H7121"\w* \w Hilkiah|strong="H2518"\w*’s \w son|strong="H1121"\w* Eliakim, \w who|strong="H1931"\w* \w has|strong="H1961"\w* \w served|strong="H1961"\w* \w serve|strong="H1961"\w* \w me|strong="H7121"\w* \add well\add*, \w to|strong="H1961"\w* replace \w you|strong="H3117"\w*.  
\v 21 \w I|strong="H5414"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w allow|strong="H5414"\w* \w him|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w wear|strong="H3847"\w* \w your|strong="H5414"\w* \w robe|strong="H3801"\w*, \w and|strong="H3063"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w fasten|strong="H5414"\w* \w your|strong="H5414"\w* sash \w around|strong="H3027"\w* \w him|strong="H5414"\w*, \w and|strong="H3063"\w* \w I|strong="H5414"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w give|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w him|strong="H5414"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* \w authority|strong="H3027"\w* \w that|strong="H5414"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* \w had|strong="H1961"\w*. \w He|strong="H1004"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* \w like|strong="H1961"\w* [MET] \w a|strong="H3068"\w* father \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* \w people|strong="H3427"\w* \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w Jerusalem|strong="H3389"\w* \w and|strong="H3063"\w* \add all the other\add* towns \w in|strong="H3427"\w* \w Judah|strong="H3063"\w*.  
\v 22 \w I|strong="H5414"\w* \w will|strong="H1004"\w* \w give|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w him|strong="H5414"\w* \w authority|strong="H5921"\w* [MTY] \w over|strong="H5921"\w* \add what happens in\add* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w palace|strong="H1004"\w* \w where|strong="H1004"\w* \w King|strong="H5921"\w* \w David|strong="H1732"\w* \add lived\add*; \w when|strong="H5921"\w* \w he|strong="H1004"\w* decides something [MET], \w no|strong="H5414"\w* \w one|strong="H1004"\w* \w will|strong="H1004"\w* \w be|strong="H5414"\w* able \w to|strong="H5921"\w* oppose \w it|strong="H5414"\w*; \w when|strong="H5921"\w* \w he|strong="H1004"\w* refuses \w to|strong="H5921"\w* do something, \w no|strong="H5414"\w* \w one|strong="H1004"\w* \w will|strong="H1004"\w* \w be|strong="H5414"\w* able \w to|strong="H5921"\w* force \w him|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* do \w it|strong="H5414"\w*.  
\v 23 \w I|strong="H1961"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w cause|strong="H1961"\w* \w his|strong="H1961"\w* \w family|strong="H1004"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* greatly respected, because \w I|strong="H1961"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* put \w him|strong="H8628"\w* firmly \w in|strong="H1004"\w* \w his|strong="H1961"\w* \w position|strong="H3678"\w* \add as supervisor of the workers in the palace\add*, \w like|strong="H1961"\w* [SIM] \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w nail|strong="H3489"\w* \w that|strong="H1004"\w* \w is|strong="H1961"\w* firmly hammered \w into|strong="H1961"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* wall.  
\v 24 Others \w will|strong="H1004"\w* enable \w him|strong="H5921"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w have|strong="H3605"\w* \w much|strong="H5921"\w* \w responsibility|strong="H5921"\w*, \w with|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* result \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w members|strong="H1004"\w* \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* \w family|strong="H1004"\w*, \w even|strong="H5704"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* most insignificant ones, \w will|strong="H1004"\w* \w be|strong="H1004"\w* \w honored|strong="H3519"\w*.' ”   
\p
\v 25  \add But\add* \w the|strong="H5002"\w* Commander \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H5002"\w* \w armies|strong="H6635"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* angels \w also|strong="H3068"\w* \w says|strong="H5002"\w*, “\add Shebna is like\add* [MET] \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w peg|strong="H3489"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* firmly \w fastened|strong="H8628"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w the|strong="H5002"\w* wall. \w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w there|strong="H3117"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w be|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w time|strong="H3117"\w* \w when|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \add remove him from his position\add*; \w he|strong="H1931"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w lose|strong="H3772"\w* \w his|strong="H3068"\w* power/influence, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* everything \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w he|strong="H1931"\w* promoted [MET] \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w fail|strong="H3772"\w*. \add That will surely happen\add* \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \add I\add*, \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w*, \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w it|strong="H1931"\w*.”   
\c 23  
\s1 A message about Tyre’s punishment  
\p
\v 1  \add I received\add* \w this|strong="H3588"\w* \w message|strong="H4853"\w* \add from Yahweh\add* \w about|strong="H4853"\w* \w Tyre|strong="H6865"\w* \add city\add*:  
\q1 \w You|strong="H3588"\w* \add sailors on\add* [APO] ships \w from|strong="H1540"\w* \w Tarshish|strong="H8659"\w*,  
\q2 weep, \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \add the harbor of\add* \w Tyre|strong="H6865"\w* \w and|strong="H1004"\w* \w all|strong="H1540"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w houses|strong="H1004"\w* \add in the city\add* \w have|strong="H3588"\w* been \w destroyed|strong="H7703"\w*.  
\q2 \w The|strong="H3588"\w* reports \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w heard|strong="H3588"\w* \w in|strong="H1004"\w* \w Cyprus|strong="H3794"\w* \add island\add* \w about|strong="H4853"\w* \w Tyre|strong="H6865"\w* \add are true\add*.   
\b  
\q1
\v 2 \w You|strong="H3427"\w* \w people|strong="H3427"\w* \w who|strong="H3427"\w* \w live|strong="H3427"\w* \w along|strong="H5674"\w* \w the|strong="H5674"\w* coast \add near Tyre\add*, \w and|strong="H3427"\w* \w merchants|strong="H5503"\w* \w of|strong="H3427"\w* \w Sidon|strong="H6721"\w* \add city\add*, mourn \w silently|strong="H1826"\w*.  
\q2 \w Your|strong="H5674"\w* sailors \w went|strong="H5674"\w* \w across|strong="H5674"\w* \w the|strong="H5674"\w* \w seas|strong="H3220"\w* \add to many places like Tyre\add*.   
\q1
\v 3 \w They|strong="H1471"\w* sailed across deep seas  
\q2 \w to|strong="H1961"\w* buy \w grain|strong="H2233"\w* \w in|strong="H7227"\w* Egypt  
\q2 \w and|strong="H1471"\w* \add other\add* \w crops|strong="H8393"\w* \w that|strong="H1471"\w* \w are|strong="H1471"\w* \w grown|strong="H1961"\w* along \w the|strong="H1961"\w* \w Nile|strong="H2975"\w* \add River\add*.  
\q1 Tyre \w became|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H1961"\w* city where \w people|strong="H1471"\w* \w from|strong="H1471"\w* \add all\add* \w nations|strong="H1471"\w* bought \w and|strong="H1471"\w* \w sold|strong="H1961"\w* goods.   
\b  
\q1
\v 4 \w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w now|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w people|strong="H3808"\w* \w in|strong="H3220"\w* \w Sidon|strong="H6721"\w* \w should|strong="H3588"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* ashamed,  
\q2 \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \add you trusted in Tyre\add*, \w which|strong="H3588"\w* \w has|strong="H3588"\w* \w been|strong="H3808"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w strong|strong="H4581"\w* \w fortress|strong="H4581"\w* \add on an island\add* \w in|strong="H3220"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w sea|strong="H3220"\w*.  
\q1 \add Tyre is like a woman who is saying\add*,  
\q2 “\add Now it is as though\add* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w have|strong="H3588"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w given|strong="H3205"\w* \w birth|strong="H3205"\w* \w to|strong="H3205"\w* \add any\add* \w children|strong="H3205"\w*,  
\q2 \w or|strong="H3808"\w* \w raised|strong="H7311"\w* \add any\add* \w sons|strong="H3205"\w* \w or|strong="H3808"\w* daughters.”   
\b  
\q1
\v 5 When \add the people of\add* \w Egypt|strong="H4714"\w* \w hear|strong="H8088"\w* what \w has|strong="H4714"\w* happened \w to|strong="H4714"\w* \w Tyre|strong="H6865"\w*,  
\q2 they \w will|strong="H4714"\w* grieve very much.   
\q1
\v 6 Sail \w to|strong="H5674"\w* \w Tarshish|strong="H8659"\w* \add and tell them what happened\add*;  
\q2 weep, \w you|strong="H3427"\w* \w people|strong="H3427"\w* \w who|strong="H3427"\w* \w live|strong="H3427"\w* \w along|strong="H5674"\w* \w the|strong="H5674"\w* coast.   
\q1
\v 7  \add The people in\add* \w the|strong="H3117"\w* very \w old|strong="H6924"\w* \w city|strong="H6927"\w* \add of Tyre\add* \w were|strong="H3117"\w* [RHQ] previously joyful.  
\q2 Traders [PRS] \w from|strong="H3117"\w* Tyre established colonies \w in|strong="H3117"\w* many \w distant|strong="H7350"\w* nations.   
\q1
\v 8 People \w from|strong="H5921"\w* \w Tyre|strong="H6865"\w* appointed kings \add over other places\add*;  
\q2 \w their|strong="H5921"\w* \w traders|strong="H5503"\w* \w were|strong="H8269"\w* \w wealthy|strong="H3513"\w*;  
\q1 \w they|strong="H5921"\w* \w were|strong="H8269"\w* \add as powerful and wealthy as\add* [MET] kings.  
