\c 29  
\s1 Warnings for Jerusalem  
\p
\v 1  \add This is a message from Yahweh:\add*  
\q1 Terrible things \w will|strong="H5595"\w* happen \w to|strong="H5921"\w* Jerusalem, \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w city|strong="H7151"\w* \w where|strong="H5921"\w* \add King\add* \w David|strong="H1732"\w* lived.  
