\q1
\v 2 \w But|strong="H1961"\w* \w I|strong="H1961"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w cause|strong="H1961"\w* \w you|strong="H1961"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* experience \w a|strong="H3068"\w* great disaster,  
\q2 \add and when that happens\add*,  
