\q1
\v 4 \w Then|strong="H1961"\w* \w you|strong="H1696"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w talk|strong="H1696"\w* \add as though you were\add* buried deep \w in|strong="H1696"\w* \w the|strong="H1961"\w* \w ground|strong="H6083"\w* [DOU];  
