\q2 \w with|strong="H5973"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w strong|strong="H1419"\w* wind \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* big \w storm|strong="H5591"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* fire \w that|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* burn \w up|strong="H6485"\w* everything.   
