\v 10 \w Because|strong="H3588"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w has|strong="H3068"\w* prevented \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w prophets|strong="H5030"\w* [DOU] \w from|strong="H5921"\w* understanding \add and telling you his messages\add*,  
\q2 \add it is as though\add* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* \w has|strong="H3068"\w* caused \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w be|strong="H3068"\w* fast/deeply asleep.   
\b  
\p
\v 11  \add Yahweh gave me\add* \w this|strong="H2088"\w* \w vision|strong="H2380"\w*; \add but\add* \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w*, \w it|strong="H5414"\w* \w is|strong="H2088"\w* \w only|strong="H3588"\w* \w words|strong="H1697"\w* \w on|strong="H1961"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w scroll|strong="H5612"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H2088"\w* \w sealed|strong="H2856"\w* \w shut|strong="H2856"\w*. \w If|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* \w give|strong="H5414"\w* \w it|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H3201"\w* \w those|strong="H3605"\w* \w who|strong="H3605"\w* \w can|strong="H3201"\w* \w read|strong="H7121"\w* \add and request that they read it\add*, \w they|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w say|strong="H1697"\w*, “\w We|strong="H3588"\w* \w cannot|strong="H3808"\w* \w read|strong="H7121"\w* \w it|strong="H5414"\w* \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w scroll|strong="H5612"\w* \w is|strong="H2088"\w* \w sealed|strong="H2856"\w*.”  
\v 12 \w When|strong="H5921"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* \w give|strong="H5414"\w* \w it|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \add others\add* \w who|strong="H2088"\w* \w cannot|strong="H3808"\w* \w read|strong="H7121"\w*, \w they|strong="H3808"\w* \w will|strong="H5414"\w* say, “\add We cannot read it because\add* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w do|strong="H4994"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w know|strong="H3045"\w* \w how|strong="H3045"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w read|strong="H7121"\w*.”   
\p
